videos.description: Kasiyahna Kushkituah says playing physical is her game, so it was fun to play Missouri in a dogfight.
videos.headline: Kushkituah says playing physical is fun for her

videos.description: Despite trailing the 11-seed Tigers by 13 points in the first half, the 6-seed Lady Vols hold Mizzou to 17 second-half points and pull away 64-51.
videos.headline: Tennessee erases 13-point deficit to surge past Mizzou
